Package pulse.math

Class ParameterVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • pulse.math.linear.Vector
      • pulse.math.ParameterVector
  • public class ParameterVector
extends Vector
    A wrapper subclass that assigns NumericPropertyKeywords to specific components of the vector. Used when constructing the optimisation vector.
